latestIgtvVideos.caption:
In collaboration with @vareybotanics 

1. Face serum : Vit C face serum from @vareybotanics 
It’s 100% Ayurvedic with the goodness of Manjista.🥰
(It’s available in @amazondotin you can  order yours there )

2 . Eye cream : @dotandkey.skincare 👀

I hope this helps you !

latestIgtvVideos.title: My regular No makeup -Makeup look 💄
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
I am very lazy when it comes to applying makeup.So, this is my go to makeup look with minimum makeup . I have used——

1: Attitude Suncreen by @amwayofficialindia 

2: Lakmé 9 to 5 CC complexion care -shade (bronze) by @lakmeindia 

3:eyebrow pencil from @nykaabeauty 

4:lipstick- Lakmé 9 to 5 weightless matte mousse , lip and cheek colour by @lakmeindia , 

5: For eyes - the rocket volume express from  @maybelline 

6: I have used Lakmé 9 to 5 matte mousse lipstick for both eyes ,cheeks and lips by @lakmeindia , SHADE - Fuchsia Suede

7: Lip balm : lip balm ( sugared rose petal with organic Bees wax) from @forestessentials 

Do let me know in the comments down below how do you like the look 😊
